import axios from 'axios'; import React, { useState } from 'react'; import { Link, useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom'; import Swal from 'sweetalert2'; function Login() { const [loginemail, setLoginEmail] = useState(''); const [loginpass, setLoginPass] = useState(''); const [errorMessage, setErrorMessage] = useState(''); const navigate = useNavigate(); const loginrecord = () => { axios.post('http://localhost:4000/login', { loginemail, loginpass }).then( result => { console.log(result); if (result.data === 'userdata') { navigate('/userdashboard'); } else if (result.data === 'exhibitordata') { navigate('/exhibitordashboard'); } else { // Handle case where neither 'userdata' nor 'exhibitordata' is returned Swal.fire({ icon: 'error', title: 'Oops...', text: 'No user found with this email and password!', }); } }, error => { // Handle errors from the backend if (error.response.status === 400) { setErrorMessage(error.response.data.error); Swal.fire({ icon: 'error', title: 'Oops...', text: errorMessage, }); } } ); }; return(
